<title>
Timing Chain Cover Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B1406018">Timing Chain Cover Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1406019001">
<title>
Oil Seal
</title>
<ptxt>
Check oil seal lip for fault or other damage.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Replace oil seal if any abnormalities are found.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1406019002">
<title>
Timing Chain Cover
</title>
<ptxt>
Inspect oil passage (1) for VVT actuators and strainers (2).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Clean oil passage and strainers if clogging or foreign matter exists.
</ptxt>
